He doesn't seem to be very inspired.

01:34:48.000 --> 01:34:51.000
Maybe he is just here

01:34:51.000 --> 01:34:54.000
until he finds another place.

01:34:54.000 --> 01:34:57.000
This is also a very important point.

01:34:57.000 --> 01:35:00.000
It is the point that determines a manager.

01:35:00.000 --> 01:35:03.000
A vision is a manager.

01:35:03.000 --> 01:35:06.000
Of course, employees must also take part

01:35:06.000 --> 01:35:09.000
in its formation.

01:35:09.000 --> 01:35:12.000
But a priori, it is a manager's function.

01:35:12.000 --> 01:35:15.000
Coaching can be very useful here.

01:35:15.000 --> 01:35:18.000
We talked about coaching for a manager

01:35:18.000 --> 01:35:21.000
who conducts professional coaching.

01:35:21.000 --> 01:35:24.000
But if we think about the fact

01:35:24.000 --> 01:35:27.000
that there is no coaching in the company

01:35:27.000 --> 01:35:30.000
at the moment,

01:35:30.000 --> 01:35:33.000
there are several managers

01:35:33.000 --> 01:35:36.000
who already have some basic knowledge

01:35:36.000 --> 01:35:39.000
and coaching skills.

01:35:39.000 --> 01:35:42.000
Can they conduct coaching for each other?

01:35:42.000 --> 01:35:45.000
They can.

01:35:45.000 --> 01:35:48.000
But there are also some points

01:35:48.000 --> 01:35:51.000
that should be taken into account.

01:35:51.000 --> 01:35:54.000
Coaching will be effective for two managers

01:35:54.000 --> 01:35:57.000
only when they work

01:35:58.000 --> 01:36:01.000
within the same organization.

01:36:01.000 --> 01:36:04.000
When their status in the company

01:36:04.000 --> 01:36:07.000
is approximately equal.

01:36:07.000 --> 01:36:10.000
It should not be a general manager

01:36:10.000 --> 01:36:13.000
and a warehouse manager.

01:36:13.000 --> 01:36:16.000
It should be a commercial manager

01:36:16.000 --> 01:36:19.000
or a executive manager.

01:36:19.000 --> 01:36:22.000
These are people who are on the same hierarchy.

01:36:22.000 --> 01:36:25.000
Again, if one of the managers

01:36:26.000 --> 01:36:29.000
decides that he needs a coach,

01:36:29.000 --> 01:36:32.000
he needs a person

01:36:32.000 --> 01:36:35.000
with whom he can discuss everything,

01:36:35.000 --> 01:36:38.000
someone he can trust,

01:36:38.000 --> 01:36:41.000
and the same person

01:36:41.000 --> 01:36:44.000
who has information about this organization.

01:36:44.000 --> 01:36:47.000
Here, too, it is necessary to be guided

01:36:47.000 --> 01:36:50.000
by the fact that the coach, the manager

01:36:50.000 --> 01:36:53.000
and the manager who needs coaching

01:36:53.000 --> 01:36:56.000
are different people.

01:36:56.000 --> 01:36:59.000
If one of them is fast, active

01:36:59.000 --> 01:37:02.000
and the other is slow and calm,

01:37:02.000 --> 01:37:05.000
it is unlikely that they will be comfortable

01:37:05.000 --> 01:37:08.000
conducting a coaching session.

01:37:08.000 --> 01:37:11.000
If you need coaching as a manager,

01:37:11.000 --> 01:37:14.000
try to find a manager

01:37:14.000 --> 01:37:17.000
of your organization

01:37:17.000 --> 01:37:20.000
who is about the same as you

01:37:20.000 --> 01:37:23.000
Think about who you could trust,

01:37:23.000 --> 01:37:26.000
who you could be sincere with,

01:37:26.000 --> 01:37:29.000
who you could discuss the issues

01:37:29.000 --> 01:37:32.000
that are really important to you,

01:37:32.000 --> 01:37:35.000
who from the managers of your company

01:37:35.000 --> 01:37:38.000
you would like to get feedback from,

01:37:38.000 --> 01:37:41.000
how to evaluate your activities

01:37:41.000 --> 01:37:44.000
in order to correct your actions

01:37:44.000 --> 01:37:47.000
and be more effective later.

01:37:47.000 --> 01:37:50.000
And, of course, if such interaction

01:37:50.000 --> 01:37:53.000
will take place,

01:37:53.000 --> 01:37:56.000
it is rather a sign of your success,

01:37:56.000 --> 01:37:59.000
a sign of your development,

01:37:59.000 --> 01:38:02.000
when you, as a person, are ready

01:38:02.000 --> 01:38:05.000
to trust,

01:38:05.000 --> 01:38:08.000
to work on yourself

01:38:08.000 --> 01:38:11.000
and to share the information

01:38:11.000 --> 01:38:14.000
that concerns you

01:38:14.000 --> 01:38:17.000
and to be ready to receive feedback.

01:38:17.000 --> 01:38:20.000
Even developing feedback

01:38:20.000 --> 01:38:23.000
may not always be pleasant,

01:38:23.000 --> 01:38:26.000
but it is important and necessary

01:38:26.000 --> 01:38:29.000
to correct your actions

01:38:29.000 --> 01:38:32.000
and to be more effective later.

01:38:44.000 --> 01:38:47.000
So, today we have discussed

01:38:47.000 --> 01:38:50.000
some blocks of coaching

01:38:50.000 --> 01:38:53.000
in the management of changes.

01:38:53.000 --> 01:38:56.000
I would like to briefly summarize

01:38:56.000 --> 01:38:59.000
that coaching is really

01:38:59.000 --> 01:39:02.000
a very strong and powerful tool

01:39:02.000 --> 01:39:05.000
in managing changes in the company.

01:39:05.000 --> 01:39:08.000
Those organizations that have already

01:39:08.000 --> 01:39:11.000
introduced this method

01:39:11.000 --> 01:39:14.000
for their team members

01:39:14.000 --> 01:39:17.000
really get great results.

01:39:17.000 --> 01:39:20.000
People like to work in the company

01:39:20.000 --> 01:39:23.000
that interests them.

01:39:23.000 --> 01:39:26.000
People work with more dedication

01:39:26.000 --> 01:39:29.000
in the company where they are listened to,

01:39:29.000 --> 01:39:32.000
where they are perceived

01:39:32.000 --> 01:39:35.000
and where they get positive feedback.

01:39:35.000 --> 01:39:38.000
As you have already understood,

01:39:38.000 --> 01:39:41.000
coaching can be done

01:39:41.000 --> 01:39:44.000
at the level of a subordinate manager

01:39:44.000 --> 01:39:47.000
or a subordinate subordinate

01:39:47.000 --> 01:39:50.000
or a manager manager.

01:39:50.000 --> 01:39:53.000
You just need to act

01:39:53.000 --> 01:39:56.000
based on the coaching principles

01:39:56.000 --> 01:39:59.000
that we have discussed.

01:39:59.000 --> 01:40:02.000
So, today we have discussed

01:40:02.000 --> 01:40:05.000
the coaching of organizational changes.

01:40:06.000 --> 01:40:09.000
I sincerely wish you

01:40:09.000 --> 01:40:12.000
to use these methods

01:40:12.000 --> 01:40:15.000
and to get great results.

01:40:15.000 --> 01:40:18.000
After all, every company

01:40:18.000 --> 01:40:21.000
that introduces this method

01:40:21.000 --> 01:40:24.000
really achieves success.

01:40:24.000 --> 01:40:27.000
You can already use this knowledge,

01:40:27.000 --> 01:40:30.000
develop these skills in yourself

01:40:30.000 --> 01:40:33.000
and apply them to your organization.

